{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00115/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00115"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:01:15"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman sitting in an armchair by a fire speaks to someone offscreen."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00115","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00115"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1/714f4bc0-717a-4f06-a33b-9801b1d5cd47","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:39:02.298Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The camera slowly zooms out, which creates distance with Alma as she tells her interlocutor about her reciprocal relationship with Reynolds. “Maybe he is the most demanding man,” she claims, as she remains at the center of the frame. This opening scene and the central role she plays in it (both literally and figuratively) foreshadows the final plot point, which reveals an unusual and unexpected power relationship between Alma and Reynolds.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:772.4227941176471,45.94852941176459,913.7205882352941,1012.1691176470588"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1/57b43963-dd16-4556-a488-ae31033709a9","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:40:03.678Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds is properly identified as a “demanding” man, as his first interaction with Alma involves a lengthy, complicated breakfast order at the café at which she works. Alma, however, is more than up for the challenge.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:21.40808823529415,53.24999999999996,196.8088235294117,142.58823529411757"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1/5341d098-c5a7-4078-9491-3b9625f744f3","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:40:42.014Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>With Dr. Hardy speaking from off camera, audiences are left uncertain whom Alma is addressing, bringing them into the conversation as stand-in participants with the scene shot as if Alma is speaking to them.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00115/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:30.88235294117652,229.14705882352928,189.47426470588226,152.11764705882354"}}}]}]}]}